{"tid":1524614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠係好想大家勇武","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:43:36.000Z","uid":132430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3954e7fdb139319e6f2763c9a991a059ace5e1df","tid":1524614,"uid":132430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/31/P2019083100919.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F31%2FP2019083100919.htm&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=4a1b75df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/31/P2019083100919.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n激進示威者的違法及暴力行為持續升級，罔顧市民大眾的安全，特區政府予以嚴厲譴責，警方亦必定嚴正追究。特區政府將繼續維護法治，並且再次呼籲廣大市民一同向暴力說「不」，讓社會盡快回復秩序。 <br />\n <br />\n政府最想有暴力有衝突。原因係警民衝突，市民受傷既機會最大，警察有裝有盾有棍有槍有，而林奠只係睇住電視機。勇武老實亦都令林奠有機會喘一口氣。政府根本一概不理始未，一旦有肢體衝突政府就會聚焦。原本政府管治威嚴蕩然無存，一旦有暴力，林奠就可以爭取返啲機會譴責示威者，令自己既暴政合理。"},{"pid":"8b7857eba30858dd62ceb5b9b987302aaa5fd24f","tid":1524614,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:41:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721/831無獎問答遊戲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H8DUzH7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH8DUzH7.jpg&h=4b81709e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lxqsagt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxqsagt.jpg&h=281798cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">試分辨以上事件</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">都一樣，係無差別攻擊！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YqzkvvH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYqzkvvH.jpg&h=849fcb35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月，機場見！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3c0d62bbbb2b59a0198ffe8a5b3f13dc0b7b634","tid":1524614,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:41:56.000Z","msg":"［文宣超新星爆炸］ 魔警阻止人道救援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fc6u8zM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFc6u8zM.jpg&h=87ac8fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F110776013598523%2Fposts%2F125201912155933%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70okJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=2094462f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/110776013598523/posts/125201912155933?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n好撚唔人道 係咪可以推到班撚樣上軍事法庭<br />\nSorry P牌每日一post 有冇手足幫手開post"},{"pid":"444e54e5a3b8c95c4037f08266941aeac5ed1c7f","tid":1524614,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:43:36.000Z","msg":"【緊急】［蘋果/立場記者請即入］今晚警察831記者會必問 - 極重要<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524570</a>"}]}